1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,110
(Child actors were accompanied
by a guardian...)

2
00:00:02,170 --> 00:00:03,810
(and filmed in a safe,
supervised environment.)

3
00:00:04,810 --> 00:00:07,210
You're sad that Mr. Yang
is going on a trip, aren't you?

4
00:00:07,210 --> 00:00:08,380
Of course I am.

5
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:12,080
Hold on. Which way do we go?

6
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:19,120
My goodness.

7
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:31,740
Goodness.

8
00:00:35,810 --> 00:00:37,080
We'll go in now.

9
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:41,680
Seon Chul...

10
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:43,420
Seon Chul.

11
00:00:45,750 --> 00:00:47,690
You said you were going on a trip.
Why are you in the hospital?

12
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:50,020
Well, about that...

13
00:00:52,790 --> 00:00:53,860
Oh no, I'm busted.

14
00:00:54,330 --> 00:00:55,330
Mr. Yang.

15
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:57,800
What's wrong?

16
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:08,810
What? Leukemia?

17
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:12,280
So what are you doing
here in the hospital?

18
00:01:13,210 --> 00:01:14,210
Well...

19
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:17,250
They suggested
a bone marrow transplant.

20
00:01:17,550 --> 00:01:19,580
Of course you should do it,
Mr. Yang.

21
00:01:19,950 --> 00:01:21,520
At my age, it's...

22
00:01:22,250 --> 00:01:24,190
They said they don't know
if I'll live...

23
00:01:24,260 --> 00:01:25,860
or die even with the transplant.

24
00:01:28,890 --> 00:01:30,060
So for now,

25
00:01:30,730 --> 00:01:32,900
I decided to just hold
out with chemotherapy.

26
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,270
Ju Ah,

27
00:01:35,970 --> 00:01:38,200
your granddaughter,
called 911 for me.

28
00:01:38,270 --> 00:01:40,710
Thanks to her, I made
it to the hospital.

29
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,580
But Hyun Bin found me out.

30
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,210
How could this happen?

31
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:49,510
It's because I've sinned so much.

32
00:01:50,980 --> 00:01:52,780
Don't say that.

33
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:55,320
Hey, does that make
everyone here a sinner?

34
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:57,120
And this is a prison?

35
00:02:00,190 --> 00:02:01,560
How can you be laughing?

36
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,830
Hey, I'm laughing
because you're here.

37
00:02:04,730 --> 00:02:07,570
Is this why you told me to
take care of all your kids?

38
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,930
Yes, you found me out.

39
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:10,700
Gosh.

40
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:14,570
- You have to tell the kids.
- No.

41
00:02:15,970 --> 00:02:17,910
Dong Suk is trying for a baby,

42
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:20,480
and Dong Ik has
an election coming up,

43
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,180
so I don't want them to worry.

44
00:02:23,250 --> 00:02:24,250
And Hyun Bin,

45
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:26,780
he's going on blind dates,

46
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,620
and we decided
he should get married soon.

47
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:31,790
I need to get it all done
quickly and go to In Ok.

48
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,760
I have to go to In Ok.

49
00:02:35,130 --> 00:02:38,430
Oh, come on. Why would you say that?

50
00:02:38,730 --> 00:02:41,870
In Ok would want you to stay
with the kids for a long time.

51
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:46,300
Just think positive thoughts.
That's how you'll get better.

52
00:02:52,010 --> 00:02:59,020
(Hanguk University Hospital)

53
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:05,620
You're feeling down, aren't you?

54
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:09,960
I'll be checking in on him,
so don't worry too much.

55
00:03:11,530 --> 00:03:13,100
It's so heartbreaking.

56
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:17,670
First Dong Suk, and now Dr. Yang.

57
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,210
In Ok passed away like that,

58
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:24,010
and now Mr. Yang is sick too.

59
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:27,550
We have to take good care of them.

60
00:03:28,780 --> 00:03:30,580
As if they were all my own children.

61
00:03:32,850 --> 00:03:33,850
Yes.

62
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:37,160
We should.

63
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:42,730
(Hanguk University Hospital)

64
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:48,300
I got some tickets to a play.
Want to go with me, Eun Bin?

65
00:03:48,930 --> 00:03:49,930
Eun Bin?

66
00:03:52,100 --> 00:03:54,670
Well, it's just...

67
00:03:58,010 --> 00:03:59,010
Aunt...

68
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:01,410
Are you dating Eun Bin?

69
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,850
No, we're not dating.

70
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,650
Then why are you two
going to a play?

71
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,890
Well, you see...

72
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:14,190
I like Eun Bin.

73
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:16,860
What?

74
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:19,630
I'm sorry, Aunt.

75
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:26,840
Wow, Eun Bin must be thrilled.
She's finally won your heart.

76
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:31,540
But I don't think Eun Bin knows
how I feel yet.

77
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:33,910
Oh my, so are you going to confess?

78
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:38,480
I shouldn't, right?
Since we're, you know, in-laws.

79
00:04:40,690 --> 00:04:42,890
Honestly, I see it
a little differently.

80
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:45,260
It's not like it's a legal issue,

81
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:47,230
and it's not as if you two are
getting married right away.

82
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:50,190
- So...
- Just go for it.

83
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:52,330
I'll talk to your uncle about it.

84
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:55,100
- Really?
- Yes.

85
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:58,840
Falling for someone you know
you're not supposed to be with...

86
00:04:59,170 --> 00:05:00,770
I know that feeling all too well.

87
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:04,380
Thank you, Aunt.

88
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:13,950
Great work. Have a good night.

89
00:05:16,790 --> 00:05:18,020
Sorry we got cut off.

90
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:20,360
Want to go see
a late-night play today?

91
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:25,130
What is this? Why ask me to see
a play all of a sudden?

92
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:31,800
- Here you go.
- You're so lucky.

93
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:36,670
- But are you going like that?
- What's wrong with how I look?

94
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:44,180
You look totally ragged and messy.

95
00:05:49,490 --> 00:05:51,220
I'll touch up your makeup for you.

96
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:54,130
Should we pick something
from the sponsored clothes too?

97
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:58,430
Really? Wow, thank you! Wow!

98
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,960
You said you're going
to a play, right?

99
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:29,930
Wow. Didn't you just come from work?

100
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:31,600
Why do you look so pretty?

101
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:35,930
What do you mean?
I just came as usual.

102
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:41,670
No, really. Your eyeliner
is different too.

103
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:46,040
What? You said you didn't even
know what eyeliner was before.

104
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,810
Hey, I noticed back then too,
you know.

105
00:06:47,810 --> 00:06:49,610
I just pretended I didn't.

106
00:06:51,250 --> 00:06:52,250
Let's go in.

107
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:55,590
Are you asking me to hold your hand?

108
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:59,920
No, I came earlier and saw
there are a lot of stairs.

109
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:02,490
And you're wearing heels. So...

110
00:07:04,100 --> 00:07:05,960
Should I take it then?

111
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:16,470
- Let's go.
- Okay.

112
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:28,820
Then I'm ordering this bed, okay?

113
00:07:30,450 --> 00:07:33,090
What? Yes, sure.
Order whichever one you like.

114
00:07:34,690 --> 00:07:36,230
Is something wrong, honey?

115
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:41,170
What do I do?

116
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:43,500
Bucket's approval rating...

117
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:45,940
is 0.3 percent.

118
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:51,310
- What? Zero point three?
- I talked a big game,

119
00:07:51,410 --> 00:07:54,110
but I'm so worried,
I have no idea what to do.

120
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:56,250
Wait, but they've
already done a poll?

121
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,580
He hasn't even registered
as a candidate.

122
00:07:58,620 --> 00:08:01,720
I think Councilor Hwang ran one
on purpose.

123
00:08:02,550 --> 00:08:05,690
- Councilor Hwang must be nervous.
- What?

124
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:08,430
With someone as popular
as you by Bucket's side,

125
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:12,830
- he must be panicking.
- No, he's not panicking.

126
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:16,170
It's not 3. It's 0.3.

127
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:19,500
Dr. Gong, you have to
start from the bottom...

128
00:08:19,570 --> 00:08:21,710
to enjoy the climb to the top.

129
00:08:21,770 --> 00:08:24,240
This isn't the bottom,
this is the basement.

130
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:27,080
What can we possibly do
to climb out of this?

131
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:30,250
Instead of trying to do something,
try not to do something.

132
00:08:30,550 --> 00:08:34,090
- What shouldn't I do?
- What Bucket's wife tells him.

133
00:08:35,250 --> 00:08:36,390
Don't you remember what she did...

134
00:08:36,450 --> 00:08:38,390
during the Merchants' Association
President Election?

135
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:41,760
Colluding on rent prices,
slandering the opposing candidate...

136
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,960
She did all sorts of dirty tricks.

137
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:46,730
Right. That's true. You're right.

138
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:50,700
Stop her. If you can just rein in
Bucket's wife, you'll do fine.

139
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,500
Right, right.

140
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:56,110
Bucket must be getting
coached right now,

141
00:08:56,170 --> 00:08:57,340
I'm sure of it.

142
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:01,580
How was it?

143
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:03,550
Was it fun?

144
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:05,480
It was amazing.

145
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,320
Thank you, in-law.

146
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:14,460
That's enough.
There are no more stairs.

147
00:09:14,690 --> 00:09:16,390
Oh, right.

148
00:09:20,330 --> 00:09:21,330
Eun Bin,

149
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:24,770
my aunt found out.

150
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:26,970
What? That we saw a play?

151
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:31,210
No. The fact that I like you.

152
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,080
What?

153
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:03,740
Yes, Jeong Han. That makes sense.
Okay, I got it.

154
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,240
What are you doing, dear?

155
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:08,310
Nowadays, with ionized water,

156
00:10:08,380 --> 00:10:09,380
I heard many people
are washing fruit...

157
00:10:09,450 --> 00:10:11,980
before they eat it,
so I thought I would try it too.

158
00:10:12,950 --> 00:10:16,950
- Here, honey.
- Isn't there a knife? To peel it.

159
00:10:17,050 --> 00:10:18,590
Oh, it's fine.
I washed it thoroughly,

160
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:20,090
so you can eat it with the skin on.

161
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:21,460
Really?

162
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:24,500
Wow, it does look clean, right?

163
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,600
It's nice that it's so easy to eat.

164
00:10:29,770 --> 00:10:32,770
Honey, listen.
About your approval ratings,

165
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:35,140
I have been thinking
about a way to raise them.

166
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:39,140
The guy Councilor Hwang is backing,

167
00:10:39,210 --> 00:10:43,150
the former aide, Im Tae Gyu, right?
We find his weakness,

168
00:10:43,210 --> 00:10:44,820
and we exploit it,
and then just like that...

169
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:47,050
Are you listening?

170
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:48,750
Yes, I am listening.

171
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:52,960
But I am not going to do
what you tell me to.

172
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:57,500
What? Why not?
Honey, I'm a brilliant strategist.

173
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,960
Top Salesperson Cha Se Ri.
Have you forgotten?

174
00:11:00,230 --> 00:11:02,030
I know. I know very well.

175
00:11:02,570 --> 00:11:04,000
But I am just going to do...

176
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:06,940
what Jeong Han suggests.

177
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:11,440
Seong Mi, I mean,
Dr. Han Seong Mi said that...

178
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:14,710
as long as I stop you,
things will be fine.

179
00:11:17,050 --> 00:11:20,350
Here, it's a prescription.
A prescription for love.

180
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:27,530
You promised to respect
my opinion, right?

181
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:29,730
Please trust me.

182
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:34,770
- It's Father.
- Really? He didn't pick up before.

183
00:11:34,970 --> 00:11:37,870
Wow, he's actually
making a video call.

184
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:41,470
Oh, Father.

185
00:11:41,770 --> 00:11:43,540
Father, where are you?

186
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:46,080
I'm in Danyang.
I'm back at my hotel.

187
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,910
Oh, Father,
are you having a good time?

188
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:49,450
You weren't answering your phone.

189
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:53,080
I was fishing at the Namhan River...

190
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:56,090
and was busy
sightseeing on a cruise.

191
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:58,920
What about your meals?
Are you eating well?

192
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:02,230
I had spicy mandarin fish
stew with a glass of soju.

193
00:12:02,290 --> 00:12:05,500
Oh, Father,
you shouldn't be drinking.

194
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,030
I will do what I want.

195
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:10,330
- I'm going to bed now.
- Father, wait...

196
00:12:10,430 --> 00:12:13,900
Please be sure to call me
tomorrow, too. All right?

197
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:16,870
I miss you, Father.

198
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:33,420
What? Woo Jae confessed to you?

199
00:12:36,730 --> 00:12:38,460
That guy is hopeless.

200
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:40,460
Did he forget that
you two are in-laws?

201
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:44,240
Hey, your mom,
who is also my aunt...

202
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:48,240
and Woo Jae's aunt,
gave us her blessing.

203
00:12:48,610 --> 00:12:50,940
Really? Even as double in-laws?

204
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:54,080
Is being double in-laws
really that strange?

205
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:58,350
Well, it is a bit strange.

206
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:02,420
Look. Let's say we have a child.

207
00:13:02,950 --> 00:13:05,160
To that child, Woo Jae is
a cousin from my side,

208
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:06,890
and Eun Bin is
a cousin from your side.

209
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,190
Wouldn't it be strange...

210
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:10,630
if two of their cousins
are married to each other?

211
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:12,360
Oh, come on, they're
both still young.

212
00:13:12,430 --> 00:13:14,030
Why are you already
talking about marriage?

213
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:19,370
Oh, but are Ju Ah and Hyun Bin
completely over?

214
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:22,070
No, from what I saw
at the company dinner,

215
00:13:23,210 --> 00:13:24,340
it seemed that way.

216
00:13:25,380 --> 00:13:28,150
If they get involved too,
that would make us triple in-laws.

217
00:13:28,650 --> 00:13:30,010
Come on, surely...

218
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,850
that won't happen, right?
No, no way.

219
00:13:58,810 --> 00:14:01,380
(Director Yang Hyun Bin)

220
00:14:06,450 --> 00:14:07,950
You're already up.

221
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:10,890
I thought you'd left.

222
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:12,590
Me?

223
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:15,730
I thought you would
reconsider and decide...

224
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:17,830
you just couldn't do it,
then run away.

225
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:19,760
I told you I'm not
running away anymore.

226
00:14:19,830 --> 00:14:21,630
What, should I tie myself
to you with a rope?

227
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:27,340
But why are you covering up?

228
00:14:28,970 --> 00:14:30,270
It's just a little awkward.

229
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:36,180
Why are you being like this?
After everything.

230
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:40,550
- Don't do this.
- What? Are you getting shy?

231
00:14:40,950 --> 00:14:44,320
- You really are.
- Could you turn around?

232
00:14:45,260 --> 00:14:47,190
I guess you're
a virtuous maiden after all.

233
00:14:47,930 --> 00:14:50,660
- Why are you so bold?
- And you don't like it?

234
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:51,730
No.

235
00:14:52,830 --> 00:14:54,160
But...

236
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:57,200
Why are you up so early?

237
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,170
It's a busy day.
I have to hurry home,

238
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,770
tell my parents,
and then get to work.

239
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:04,340
- Tell them what?
- That I'm marrying you.

240
00:15:04,410 --> 00:15:05,780
Today? Right now?

241
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:09,550
Yes. We should tell them right away
and register our marriage.

242
00:15:09,780 --> 00:15:12,050
That's ridiculous.

243
00:15:12,150 --> 00:15:15,190
What is? Dragging this out
will only make things worse.

244
00:15:15,250 --> 00:15:17,720
I'll handle my family,
so you handle yours.

245
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:20,820
Goodness, you're
such a Runaway Train.

246
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:25,560
Want to see the Runaway
Train? Choo-choo, choo-choo.

247
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:31,600
What are you doing? Go and make...

248
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:33,440
your queen some hotcakes.

249
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:34,610
Yes, my lady.

250
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:39,880
- Go, go.
- Let's go.

251
00:15:40,010 --> 00:15:41,110
We don't have time.

252
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:47,180
- Did you sleep well?
- Hey.

253
00:15:47,250 --> 00:15:50,590
Father, are you helping Mother?

254
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:53,020
My dear, did you sleep well?

255
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:54,960
Yes. And you, Father?

256
00:15:55,330 --> 00:15:58,600
- I didn't sleep well.
- Why not?

257
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,430
Why do you think?

258
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:04,230
Oh, by the way, you said you were
ordering a bigger bed. Did you?

259
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:07,240
Oh, yes. It's scheduled
for delivery today.

260
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:10,440
It's a good thing I ordered it.
I would have been in trouble.

261
00:16:11,940 --> 00:16:13,510
Oh, by the way, dear.

262
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:16,510
Did you see Ju Ah
come home yesterday?

263
00:16:20,950 --> 00:16:22,220
(Dr. Han Seong Mi)

264
00:16:22,290 --> 00:16:23,290
Yes.

265
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:25,520
Yes.

266
00:16:26,190 --> 00:16:27,560
Oh, really?

267
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:29,860
Yes, I understand.

268
00:16:30,230 --> 00:16:32,660
Make sure you eat well
and take your medicine.

269
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:34,470
I'll come by after work,
Grandfather.

270
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:38,500
What is it? Did something happen?

271
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:40,870
He said Ms. Na
and your grandfather...

272
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:42,670
found out he was in the hospital.

273
00:16:43,310 --> 00:16:45,340
Really? Oh no.

274
00:16:46,210 --> 00:16:49,780
He asked them to keep it
a secret for now. He'll be fine.

275
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:59,460
Are you really going
to drop the bomb today?

276
00:16:59,820 --> 00:17:02,930
Why do you keep asking?
Are you losing your nerve?

277
00:17:03,060 --> 00:17:06,900
No, I was just wondering
if I should go in with you to help.

278
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:11,240
No, thanks. I'll handle my family,
and you handle yours.

279
00:17:12,970 --> 00:17:16,810
I haven't heard that in a while.
I love when you call me that.

280
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:21,710
Too bad. I won't be able
to call you that for long.

281
00:17:22,080 --> 00:17:23,710
Why? Why not?

282
00:17:24,280 --> 00:17:25,620
Because when we're married...

283
00:17:26,220 --> 00:17:27,850
I'll be calling you my husband.

284
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:32,190
Okay. Go on in.

285
00:17:32,260 --> 00:17:35,130
- What? I'm not finished here yet.
- What?

286
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:51,980
Oh, you scared me.

287
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,880
Grandfather.

288
00:17:56,910 --> 00:17:58,820
Isn't that Seon Chul's grandson?

289
00:17:58,980 --> 00:18:01,350
Yes, that's right, Grandfather.
Yang Hyun Bin.

290
00:18:01,820 --> 00:18:02,950
But my dear granddaughter,

291
00:18:03,490 --> 00:18:07,320
I've been locked away for 30 years,
so I may not know, but,

292
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:09,330
is this how people
say hello these days?

293
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:14,730
Like this?

294
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:17,940
No, Grandfather.

295
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:20,740
This is what you do
when you're getting married.

296
00:18:20,970 --> 00:18:22,170
Getting married?

297
00:18:23,370 --> 00:18:24,610
You're getting married?

298
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:31,350
Yes, I'm getting married.

299
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:34,520
You said you'd get a consultation
from a matchmaking agency,

300
00:18:34,590 --> 00:18:36,550
and you already found
someone you want to marry?

301
00:18:36,820 --> 00:18:37,960
I know, right?

302
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:40,160
Who is this woman that
you're in such a rush?

303
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:41,930
It's Ju Ah. Gong Ju Ah.

304
00:18:42,390 --> 00:18:43,390
What?

305
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:46,330
What? Who?

306
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:48,770
Gong Ju Ah.

307
00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:54,840
Hey, you.

308
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:58,080
You barge in here first thing
in the morning to joke around?

309
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:02,210
I'm not joking. We're doing it
as soon as possible, so you know.

310
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:04,180
Hey, hold on.

311
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:05,780
Wait a minute, Hyun Bin.

312
00:19:07,950 --> 00:19:09,520
What are you talking about?

313
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:11,560
It's exactly as I said.

314
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:14,530
I'm marrying Gong Ju Ah
as soon as possible. Period.

315
00:19:14,730 --> 00:19:17,130
But why? Why so suddenly?
You swore you two...

316
00:19:17,190 --> 00:19:21,230
had no feelings for each other.
Wait, were you lying to me?

317
00:19:21,630 --> 00:19:24,430
Wow, that Gong Ju Ah
is really something.

318
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:25,670
Why are you calling...

319
00:19:25,670 --> 00:19:27,240
your future daughter-in-law
that girl?

320
00:19:27,300 --> 00:19:28,940
Who says she's
my future daughter-in-law?

321
00:19:29,340 --> 00:19:33,010
- Now, honey, try to calm down.
- How am I supposed to calm down?

322
00:19:33,610 --> 00:19:35,750
Absolutely not. Never.

323
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:41,450
Saying no won't change anything.
I'm going to marry Hyun Bin.

324
00:19:42,690 --> 00:19:43,690
What?

325
00:19:46,490 --> 00:19:47,760
Ju Ah.

326
00:19:47,930 --> 00:19:50,790
I heard Hyun Bin was
supposed to get married...

327
00:19:50,860 --> 00:19:52,460
through an arranged date.

328
00:19:52,730 --> 00:19:55,970
Oh, I stopped him from going
on the blind date, Grandma.

329
00:19:56,230 --> 00:19:57,400
But why on earth?

330
00:19:57,530 --> 00:19:59,970
What do you mean, why?
Because I love Hyun Bin.

331
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:07,410
Are you out of your mind?

332
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:10,050
Yes. I've never been
more clearheaded.

333
00:20:10,850 --> 00:20:11,950
And...

334
00:20:12,520 --> 00:20:15,320
I stayed at Hyun Bin's
apartment with him last night.

335
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:21,360
In other words,
there's no turning back.

336
00:20:21,430 --> 00:20:22,790
So don't try to stop us.

337
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:27,230
You, come inside.

338
00:20:29,030 --> 00:20:32,700
I mean, what? How could she...

339
00:20:35,010 --> 00:20:37,910
Wow. I knew
our daughter was a handful,

340
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:39,640
but this is next level.

341
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:42,280
She's got guts.

342
00:20:43,410 --> 00:20:44,550
She takes after me.

343
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:47,820
Wow, Gong Ju Ah is awesome.

344
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:51,520
- Wow.
- I'm worried. What to do?

345
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:57,790
Hey, Seong Mi. Go easy on her, okay?

346
00:20:58,030 --> 00:21:00,230
In front of all the adults,
you said what?

347
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:04,330
You stayed at Hyun Bin's
apartment with him last night?

348
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:07,370
What's wrong with that?
We're going to get married anyway.

349
00:21:07,700 --> 00:21:09,870
Have you lost your mind?

350
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:12,280
Hey, Seong Mi. Don't get physical.

351
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:14,850
Oh, Mother, why is
she acting like this?

352
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:17,710
This stress is going
to drive me crazy.

353
00:21:18,280 --> 00:21:20,150
Don't lie. You think I don't know...

354
00:21:20,220 --> 00:21:22,450
you thrive on having
a problem to solve?

355
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:26,120
- Hey.
- You're the one who said it.

356
00:21:26,290 --> 00:21:28,090
Remember?
You told me to marry the person...

357
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,530
I can't imagine living without.

358
00:21:29,760 --> 00:21:31,960
So that gives you
the right to act so rude,

359
00:21:32,060 --> 00:21:34,970
- with no respect for propriety?
- But Ju Ah,

360
00:21:35,230 --> 00:21:37,100
what are you going to do
about Hyun Bin's family?

361
00:21:37,370 --> 00:21:39,770
Hyun Bin is telling
them himself right now.

362
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:41,440
Oh, honestly.

363
00:21:41,770 --> 00:21:45,280
How much is Bucket's wife
going to torment me now?

364
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:49,580
Mom, I'll handle it.
I'll take full responsibility.

365
00:21:49,650 --> 00:21:50,910
I'll make it work.

366
00:21:51,280 --> 00:21:52,780
You think you can make
it work just by trying?

367
00:21:53,380 --> 00:21:56,020
Do you really think they're
going to give you their blessing?

368
00:21:57,620 --> 00:22:00,320
Then we'll get married
without the blessing.

369
00:22:00,320 --> 00:22:01,390
Hey.

370
00:22:02,660 --> 00:22:05,500
Are you threatening me?

371
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:06,960
Threatening you?

372
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:10,070
I'm just telling you
how determined I am.

373
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:14,300
Are you the only one
trying and desperate again?

374
00:22:14,670 --> 00:22:17,240
Are you clinging to someone
who doesn't want you again?

375
00:22:17,570 --> 00:22:20,210
- Ju Ah feels the same way.
- Then why are you alone?

376
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:22,680
Why is she conveniently absent
for this important talk?

377
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:24,510
I was afraid
you'd pull her hair out.

378
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:25,820
She should be prepared for that.

379
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:27,680
You can't get married
without that much resolve.

380
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:30,220
Don't worry.
She's at her house right now,

381
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:32,590
telling her family
that she's marrying me.

382
00:22:35,030 --> 00:22:38,130
The kids seem to have really
made up their minds, honey.

383
00:22:38,630 --> 00:22:39,630
Right?

384
00:22:40,260 --> 00:22:41,260
Fine...

385
00:22:41,970 --> 00:22:43,170
Fine, do it.

386
00:22:43,670 --> 00:22:44,940
Do whatever you want.

387
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:48,140
Get married or don't.
Do whatever you want.

388
00:22:49,270 --> 00:22:52,040
Honey, did you just give them
your permission to marry?

389
00:22:52,110 --> 00:22:53,640
Permission?
What are you talking about?

390
00:22:53,710 --> 00:22:55,210
He said he doesn't
need my permission.

391
00:22:55,280 --> 00:22:57,910
I don't care
if they have a wedding or not.

392
00:22:57,980 --> 00:23:00,720
- I won't be going.
- Honey, come on.

393
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:02,350
We're not having a wedding.

394
00:23:02,420 --> 00:23:04,250
We're just going to
register our marriage.

395
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:07,720
Hey. Do you really want to
see Grandfather collapse?

396
00:23:07,860 --> 00:23:11,090
I'll handle Grandfather as well.
I'm going to work now.

397
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:15,230
Hyun Bin. Yang Hyun Bin.
Oh, my. I feel faint.

398
00:23:15,300 --> 00:23:17,070
- Oh no.
- Aunt, are you okay?

399
00:23:17,430 --> 00:23:21,040
Honey, I told you not to
just jump up like that. See?

400
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:23,310
Oh, what am I going to do?

401
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:08,850
Really? Gong Ju Ah put in
the code and barged in?

402
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:11,320
Yes. She came in the moment we left.

403
00:24:11,390 --> 00:24:12,690
It seems like she was tailing us.

404
00:24:13,260 --> 00:24:15,890
So she felt that way
but kept playing hard to get?

405
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:19,760
I know. Our booster plan
worked like a charm.

406
00:24:20,330 --> 00:24:22,800
And? She barged in, and then what?

407
00:24:23,370 --> 00:24:24,800
She barged in, and wait.

408
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:32,980
Wait. No. Please. Stop.

409
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:35,050
That's what she said.

410
00:24:35,950 --> 00:24:39,180
What? "Stop" what? What on earth
did she think was going to happen?

411
00:24:39,250 --> 00:24:40,720
I know, right?

412
00:24:41,150 --> 00:24:44,450
They've probably had an epic night
and gotten back together by now.

413
00:24:44,490 --> 00:24:46,760
You think so?
After they've been fighting...

414
00:24:46,820 --> 00:24:49,830
- like cats and dogs all this time?
- Want to bet?

415
00:24:49,890 --> 00:24:51,730
On whether they're
back together or not.

416
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:55,770
Well, I lose.

417
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:01,400
Oh, my.

418
00:25:05,940 --> 00:25:08,850
- What is it?
- Unbelievable. Seriously.

419
00:25:08,910 --> 00:25:10,350
Oh, come on.

420
00:25:17,820 --> 00:25:19,920
They're holding hands.

421
00:25:20,490 --> 00:25:23,430
Is the VIP guest attendance
confirmed?

422
00:25:24,230 --> 00:25:25,760
Two of them aren't attending,

423
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:28,470
so we're confirming
replacements from the waitlist.

424
00:25:28,570 --> 00:25:29,970
And the gift packages?

425
00:25:30,170 --> 00:25:33,600
The inspection is done,
and they'll all be packed today.

426
00:25:33,670 --> 00:25:37,470
- And the new product exhibition?
- The setup is almost complete,

427
00:25:37,540 --> 00:25:38,640
and we're also planning...

428
00:25:38,710 --> 00:25:40,510
to set up
a separate booth for Pelliv.

429
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:44,410
Okay. Sounds good.
Please do one last check...

430
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:46,550
so everything goes
smoothly on the day of.

431
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:49,120
- Okay.
- Thanks.

432
00:25:52,590 --> 00:25:55,660
Excuse me, you two?
Are you two dating again?

433
00:25:58,460 --> 00:26:00,560
Yes, that's right.
They're dating again.

434
00:26:02,370 --> 00:26:03,370
No.

435
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:06,070
No?

436
00:26:06,640 --> 00:26:09,110
No. We're not dating.

437
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:13,680
We're...

438
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:16,980
getting married.

439
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:24,220
Getting married?

440
00:26:24,690 --> 00:26:28,430
You're getting married?
Like, with the wedding march,

441
00:26:28,490 --> 00:26:31,800
a veil, and marching down the aisle?
That kind of married?

442
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:33,400
So it would seem.

443
00:26:33,830 --> 00:26:35,500
Oh, my.

444
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:37,870
Pacu Nacho, is this for real?

445
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:42,710
She's coming on so strong,
my head is spinning.

446
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:44,980
Ju Ah is usually very careful,

447
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:47,380
but once she makes a decision,
she never looks back.

448
00:26:47,940 --> 00:26:49,810
And who do we have to thank
for Ms. Gong's awakening?

449
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,550
It's all thanks to you, CEO.

450
00:26:54,050 --> 00:26:56,020
You were so good at pretending
to be a couple.

451
00:26:56,350 --> 00:26:59,890
I was so mad I almost grabbed
your hair, CEO or not.

452
00:27:00,560 --> 00:27:02,060
I could feel that murderous intent.

453
00:27:02,690 --> 00:27:04,790
I just knew I was going to succeed.

454
00:27:05,760 --> 00:27:08,500
This is all thanks to me,
so let me be your wedding planner.

455
00:27:08,730 --> 00:27:09,930
Please?

456
00:27:10,670 --> 00:27:14,300
But CEO, we're not
going to have a ceremony.

457
00:27:14,670 --> 00:27:16,510
That's ridiculous. Why?

458
00:27:16,770 --> 00:27:19,310
Why would you skip the biggest event
of your lives? Why?

459
00:27:19,510 --> 00:27:22,550
I appreciate the thought,
but we're kind of in a rush.

460
00:27:28,180 --> 00:27:32,390
Father, I called you so many times.
Why weren't you answering?

461
00:27:32,660 --> 00:27:36,130
Father, Dong Suk was so worried.

462
00:27:36,630 --> 00:27:40,160
Okay, I will, Father.
Make sure you eat your meals,

463
00:27:40,230 --> 00:27:43,870
and watch your step. Okay?
Oh, but when will you be back...

464
00:27:44,370 --> 00:27:45,370
Father?

465
00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:48,240
He hung up on me again.

466
00:27:49,210 --> 00:27:50,470
Good grief.

467
00:27:51,170 --> 00:27:54,740
I need to tell him about Hyun Bin,
but I don't think I can.

468
00:27:55,350 --> 00:27:58,480
Don't you be the one to tell him.
I'm sure Hyun Bin will handle it.

469
00:27:59,050 --> 00:28:02,950
Honestly, I feel awkward.
He's my nephew, after all.

470
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:06,360
And it bothers me that
the family is against it.

471
00:28:07,090 --> 00:28:10,430
- But I can't take sides either.
- I know.

472
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:13,630
This is why double in-laws
are so complicated.

473
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:18,370
My sister-in-law is sick too.
I feel terrible.

474
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,340
Goodness.

475
00:28:27,580 --> 00:28:29,450
I'm going to go see Seon Chul.

476
00:28:29,780 --> 00:28:32,450
Okay. And when you go,

477
00:28:32,550 --> 00:28:35,120
don't bring up Hyun Bin and Ju Ah.

478
00:28:35,850 --> 00:28:39,220
All right.
But Seon Chul said before...

479
00:28:39,290 --> 00:28:42,090
that he'd never allow
double in-laws.

480
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:43,760
I don't know how he'll take it.

481
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:45,800
What about you?
Are you okay with it?

482
00:28:45,930 --> 00:28:47,460
Well, it might get complicated,

483
00:28:47,500 --> 00:28:49,630
but if the kids are happy,
who are we to stop them?

484
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:53,940
It seems like they're rushing to
get married because of Seon Chul.

485
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,640
Or is it just me?

486
00:28:56,010 --> 00:28:57,970
Don't you think
it's sweet of the kids?

487
00:28:59,040 --> 00:29:02,980
We're not the problem.
The daughters-in-law are.

488
00:29:03,180 --> 00:29:04,310
Really?

489
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:07,420
We will now begin
the presentation...

490
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:09,690
of the 3H Business Briefing
event plan.

491
00:29:10,650 --> 00:29:13,460
First, our corporate vision,
and then the presentation...

492
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:16,090
Mocking someone
for being sick like that.

493
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:18,700
Do you realize
how despicable and crass that is?

494
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:21,870
If you want to be treated like
an adult, then act like one.

495
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,970
That brat. Who said she
could be my daughter-in-law?

496
00:29:24,030 --> 00:29:25,100
Who gave her the right...

497
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:36,010
Dong Suk.

498
00:29:36,580 --> 00:29:38,680
Why did you come home
instead of going to work?

499
00:29:38,750 --> 00:29:39,920
Were you worried about me?

500
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:42,320
Yes.

501
00:29:43,950 --> 00:29:48,420
I'm not against this
because I dislike Director Yang.

502
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,590
I know.

503
00:29:51,290 --> 00:29:53,800
It's because of my sister-in-law,
isn't it?

504
00:30:02,310 --> 00:30:04,740
- Who is it?
- Dong Suk, it's me.

505
00:30:06,380 --> 00:30:09,510
Why does she always show
up without calling first?

506
00:30:11,250 --> 00:30:13,850
Let her in. I'm fine.

507
00:30:23,490 --> 00:30:28,100
How many times did I tell you?
I was worried about them,

508
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:30,000
so we shouldn't let
them be so close.

509
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:33,870
- I made myself clear, didn't I?
- Are you saying this is my fault?

510
00:30:34,540 --> 00:30:36,270
You said you trusted your daughter.

511
00:30:36,340 --> 00:30:38,270
Well, look at
the result of that trust.

512
00:30:38,610 --> 00:30:40,580
This is unbelievable.

513
00:30:41,140 --> 00:30:44,210
It takes two to tango.

514
00:30:44,350 --> 00:30:49,220
My goodness. As for my Hyun Bin,
he had made up his mind.

515
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:50,620
He was going to go on blind
dates and get married,

516
00:30:50,690 --> 00:30:54,090
- this is all your daughter's fault.
- Se Ri.

517
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:57,690
My daughter gave up on
him and even quit her job.

518
00:30:57,860 --> 00:30:59,830
Your son was the one
who reached out first...

519
00:30:59,900 --> 00:31:01,760
and suggested they
be business partners.

520
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:03,600
That was about work.
If it's about work,

521
00:31:03,670 --> 00:31:05,170
then they should have just worked.

522
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:08,370
How on earth did she seduce him to
make our Hyun Bin act like this?

523
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:09,840
What? Seduce him?

524
00:31:09,910 --> 00:31:14,280
Se Ri, watch your mouth.
My gosh, this is unbelievable.

525
00:31:17,710 --> 00:31:19,880
You're right. Dong Suk, I'm sorry.

526
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:24,350
I apologize for saying
she "seduced" him.

527
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,460
But honestly,
at the formal family meeting,

528
00:31:27,490 --> 00:31:29,760
you saw how rudely
your daughter was acting toward me.

529
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:32,500
From the start,
your daughter had zero intention...

530
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:33,900
of marrying our Hyun Bin.

531
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:35,270
So what?

532
00:31:35,330 --> 00:31:37,800
This is clearly because our Hyun Bin
said he was getting married,

533
00:31:37,870 --> 00:31:38,870
and your daughter decided...

534
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:40,540
she did not want anyone
else to have him.

535
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:43,010
So she deliberately set out
to sway Hyun Bin's heart.

536
00:31:43,670 --> 00:31:46,280
All right. Let's say that's true.

537
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:50,550
Then what about your son,
who is so easily swayed?

538
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:54,280
Come on, what man wouldn't be swayed
if a woman sets her mind to it?

539
00:31:54,320 --> 00:31:55,320
That's enough.

540
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:58,050
- Unbelievable.
- Gosh, that startled me.

541
00:31:59,990 --> 00:32:00,990
Then let's do this.

542
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:05,500
I'll stop my daughter,
and you stop your son. Deal?

543
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:07,500
Fine, whatever. Let's do that.

544
00:32:08,730 --> 00:32:09,770
Is there anything else?

545
00:32:10,900 --> 00:32:13,240
Let's go.

546
00:32:13,570 --> 00:32:15,570
You'd better keep your promise,
you hear?

547
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:18,110
If you don't,
I won't sit back and do nothing.

548
00:32:18,170 --> 00:32:19,240
I will go to her office...

549
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:21,240
and rip Gong Ju Ah's hair
out of her head.

550
00:32:21,510 --> 00:32:24,450
- What did you say?
- Come on, let's go. Get up quickly.

551
00:32:24,510 --> 00:32:25,880
Hey, let go of me.

552
00:32:26,280 --> 00:32:27,650
I have no intention of accepting
her daughter...

553
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:28,720
as my daughter-in-law.

554
00:32:28,890 --> 00:32:30,850
I'm telling you,
I really can't stand Gong Ju Ah.

555
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,920
I really, really can't stand her,
you understand?

556
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:34,360
Please, stop.

557
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:35,930
My head...

558
00:32:47,870 --> 00:32:50,170
Have one more spoonful.

559
00:32:56,050 --> 00:32:57,050
This is not going to work.

560
00:33:03,790 --> 00:33:05,120
How much longer do you have?

561
00:33:05,790 --> 00:33:07,290
How am I supposed to know?

562
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:12,930
Hey, stop talking nonsense
and go get the Korean chess board.

563
00:33:14,360 --> 00:33:16,370
Are you really not going
to tell your family?

564
00:33:16,930 --> 00:33:17,930
No.

565
00:33:18,670 --> 00:33:20,440
I'm going to die either way.

566
00:33:21,870 --> 00:33:24,170
All the crying and wailing.

567
00:33:24,740 --> 00:33:25,910
I don't want to see it.

568
00:33:27,110 --> 00:33:29,710
Anyway, about my grandson.

569
00:33:30,810 --> 00:33:33,180
He suddenly said
he's bringing home his bride-to-be.

570
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:36,620
- Really?
- That's great.

571
00:33:37,250 --> 00:33:39,490
I have to get them married quickly
before I get any worse.

572
00:33:40,890 --> 00:33:42,490
He said they'll be here soon.

573
00:33:42,860 --> 00:33:45,400
You take a look too.
See if she's a decent person.

574
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:48,060
Okay.

575
00:33:51,470 --> 00:33:53,300
Oh, you were together?

576
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:55,810
- Hello.
- Grandfather.

577
00:33:55,870 --> 00:33:56,870
You're here.

578
00:33:58,140 --> 00:34:00,740
- Hello.
- How did you two come together?

579
00:34:01,140 --> 00:34:02,250
Gi Cheol's granddaughter.

580
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:04,710
Well, it's just...

581
00:34:06,250 --> 00:34:09,120
Because you called 911 for me,

582
00:34:09,290 --> 00:34:13,260
- I'm still alive. Thank you.
- Of course.

583
00:34:14,720 --> 00:34:17,860
But Hyun Bin, why is
your bride-to-be not here?

584
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:23,170
You really are clueless, aren't you?

585
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,570
Grandfather.

586
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:28,870
My bride-to-be...

587
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:33,040
is Ju Ah.

588
00:34:43,550 --> 00:34:44,590
What?

589
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:51,760
(Health Promotion Center,
Endoscopy Room)

590
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:56,970
We got his permission,
so why the long face?

591
00:34:57,330 --> 00:35:00,570
Come on, how is that permission?
It came with conditions.

592
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,670
It's conditional permission.

593
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:09,510
- Conditions? What conditions?
- Hyun Bin,

594
00:35:10,150 --> 00:35:12,150
you are to go to Mr. Gong's home...

595
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:15,420
to formally ask for his permission.

596
00:35:16,150 --> 00:35:18,290
Grandfather.
But we decided we would each...

597
00:35:18,350 --> 00:35:19,620
handle our own families.

598
00:35:19,690 --> 00:35:23,360
- That is not how it works.
- Grandfather.

599
00:35:23,430 --> 00:35:24,560
And Ju Ah...

600
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:27,860
- Me?
- Go to your future mother-in-law...

601
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:31,070
and get her to approve.

602
00:35:32,030 --> 00:35:34,640
- What?
- Grandfather.

603
00:35:40,010 --> 00:35:42,780
My mother will never approve.

604
00:35:43,510 --> 00:35:46,720
Getting my family's approval
won't be easy either.

605
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:50,750
I thought he would be against it
because we would be double in-laws,

606
00:35:50,950 --> 00:35:53,360
but he's saying something
completely out of left field.

607
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:56,590
Good grief.

608
00:35:58,730 --> 00:36:00,160
You said you were against
becoming double in-laws,

609
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:01,400
yet you gave your permission
so quickly.

610
00:36:01,660 --> 00:36:06,470
I was determined not to allow it,
over my dead body.

611
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:09,540
But when I actually thought
about dying,

612
00:36:10,370 --> 00:36:12,840
I figured there was
nothing I couldn't permit.

613
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:15,750
Right. We can worry
about our ancestors when we're dead.

614
00:36:17,510 --> 00:36:19,750
If it gets awkward,
they'll be the ones to deal with it.

615
00:36:20,950 --> 00:36:21,950
Check.

616
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:27,190
Seong Mi.

617
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:33,560
Oh, Mother. Are you home from work?

618
00:36:34,260 --> 00:36:36,800
I was sleeping
and didn't even hear you come in.

619
00:36:36,870 --> 00:36:40,740
It's all right. Stay there.
You're not sick, are you?

620
00:36:40,900 --> 00:36:44,170
Director Yang's mother
came by earlier,

621
00:36:44,170 --> 00:36:45,810
spouting all this nonsense.

622
00:36:46,380 --> 00:36:48,580
And I was so upset
I took some medicine...

623
00:36:48,640 --> 00:36:49,980
and must have dozed off.

624
00:36:51,210 --> 00:36:53,620
Yes, I heard about it.

625
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:57,390
- I'll get started on dinner.
- No.

626
00:36:57,750 --> 00:37:00,590
It's fine. We can just
have a simple meal later.

627
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:03,560
Gi Cheol has an errand today,
so he'll be late.

628
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:04,960
So just get some rest.

629
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:07,630
- Okay.
- Listen, Seong Mi.

630
00:37:10,270 --> 00:37:11,930
Hyun Bin's grandfather...

631
00:37:12,840 --> 00:37:14,770
gave his permission
for Ju Ah and Hyun Bin...

632
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:15,840
to get married.

633
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:18,670
- What?
- Yes, a moment ago...

634
00:37:18,910 --> 00:37:21,280
Gi Cheol called and told me.

635
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:24,450
I really don't know
what he was thinking...

636
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,250
He told Hyun Bin...

637
00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:30,250
to come to our house
and formally ask for our permission.

638
00:37:31,050 --> 00:37:32,760
This is driving me crazy.

639
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:36,590
And as for Ju Ah...

640
00:37:38,390 --> 00:37:40,500
he told her to win over
Hyun Bin's mother...

641
00:37:40,830 --> 00:37:42,370
and get her permission.

642
00:37:43,130 --> 00:37:44,130
He said what?

643
00:37:49,210 --> 00:37:51,240
Hey, Mom, Seong Mi.

644
00:37:51,470 --> 00:37:55,440
- You two should come out a second.
- What?

645
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:11,830
What is it you wanted to say?

646
00:38:12,860 --> 00:38:14,430
Grandmother, Uncle, Father.

647
00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:17,200
- Mother.
- "Mother?"

648
00:38:17,370 --> 00:38:19,340
- Hey, Seong Mi.
- Here.

649
00:38:20,540 --> 00:38:23,340
Please review this.
It's a son-in-law application.

650
00:38:23,770 --> 00:38:25,110
A son-in-law application?

651
00:38:25,410 --> 00:38:26,980
Yes. It details
my physical abilities,

652
00:38:27,040 --> 00:38:28,580
communication skills,
domestic skills,

653
00:38:28,840 --> 00:38:31,550
and health status,
all evaluated by category.

654
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:40,260
I thought you'd do
this your own way.

655
00:38:40,490 --> 00:38:41,720
What is all this nonsense?

656
00:38:42,630 --> 00:38:46,160
Our grandfathers
agreed to this, Mother.

657
00:38:46,260 --> 00:38:49,270
- Please stop calling me "Mother."
- Mom.

658
00:38:49,570 --> 00:38:51,800
Are you really going to
be so reckless about this?

659
00:38:52,200 --> 00:38:56,840
Wow, his stats in every category
are excellent. Outstanding.

660
00:38:56,910 --> 00:38:58,510
- They really are.
- Right?

661
00:38:58,570 --> 00:39:01,240
Sister-in-law, please try
to look on this favorably.

662
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,950
Thank you, Father, Uncle.

663
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:06,350
Are you doing this
because you knew...

664
00:39:06,420 --> 00:39:08,020
the whole family
would take your side?

665
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,490
- No, that's not it...
- Wait.

666
00:39:09,790 --> 00:39:13,720
Please give us
your blessing, Mother.

667
00:39:14,060 --> 00:39:17,460
Director Yang, don't think
you can just smooth this over.

668
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:20,930
Your mother came here again
today and caused a scene.

669
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:22,470
She did?

670
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:25,700
She said our Ju Ah seduced
you and led you on.

671
00:39:26,240 --> 00:39:28,770
- Is that true?
- Oh, no...

672
00:39:33,880 --> 00:39:37,080
Mom, I'll handle it.
I'll take care of it.

673
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,310
How will you take care of it? How?

674
00:39:38,980 --> 00:39:40,780
Director Yang's grandfather
told you...

675
00:39:40,850 --> 00:39:42,720
to get
his mother's permission, right?

676
00:39:42,990 --> 00:39:46,590
- Do you think that's possible?
- I'm telling you I'll try.

677
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:47,960
You think you can handle anything...

678
00:39:48,020 --> 00:39:49,490
because you're in
love now, don't you?

679
00:39:49,860 --> 00:39:53,200
Once you face reality, marriage is
something that won't go your way.

680
00:39:53,330 --> 00:39:54,830
Do you have any idea
how many families I've seen...

681
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:56,300
fall apart because
of conflict with in-laws?

682
00:39:56,370 --> 00:39:58,530
Seong Mi, please.

683
00:39:59,770 --> 00:40:02,000
Fine, do whatever you want.

684
00:40:02,770 --> 00:40:04,940
I don't care
if you two get married...

685
00:40:05,010 --> 00:40:07,340
or not, so just do as you please.

686
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:09,310
But I will...

687
00:40:09,810 --> 00:40:11,380
no longer consider you my daughter.

688
00:40:13,250 --> 00:40:15,080
Seong Mi, come on.
That's going too far.

689
00:40:38,540 --> 00:40:39,540
Yes?

690
00:40:41,410 --> 00:40:42,710
Yes, Father.

691
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:45,310
No, that's so unfair.

692
00:40:45,380 --> 00:40:48,050
Why should Ju Ah be
the only one making an effort?

693
00:40:48,120 --> 00:40:50,390
Director Yang's mother is
the one who's more to blame.

694
00:40:52,390 --> 00:40:54,490
Why are you laughing, Mother?

695
00:40:56,490 --> 00:41:00,360
Oh, don't worry.
Gi Cheol said he was fair about it.

696
00:41:00,930 --> 00:41:02,160
Fairly?

697
00:41:05,400 --> 00:41:06,670
What's unfair about it?

698
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:10,540
Of course it is. Why should
our Ju Ah be the only one...

699
00:41:10,610 --> 00:41:12,510
to go and appease
your daughter-in-law?

700
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:13,880
From what I've heard,

701
00:41:13,940 --> 00:41:16,310
the reason the two
daughters-in-law don't get along...

702
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:19,420
is entirely
your daughter-in-law's fault.

703
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:24,020
- So what's your point?
- I'm setting a condition too.

704
00:41:25,120 --> 00:41:26,120
What kind of condition?

705
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:30,230
Are you okay?

706
00:41:31,890 --> 00:41:33,700
Get up. Let's get something to eat.

707
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:36,430
Do you really think...

708
00:41:37,730 --> 00:41:40,640
I have any appetite right now?

709
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:45,640
Oh my goodness.

710
00:41:46,110 --> 00:41:48,340
- Father.
- Is that Father?

711
00:41:49,450 --> 00:41:53,320
Father, when are you coming back?

712
00:41:53,780 --> 00:41:55,890
Why? Is this about
Hyun Bin's marriage?

713
00:41:56,290 --> 00:41:58,790
Father, how did you know?

714
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:01,490
- Did Hyun Bin call you?
- Yes.

715
00:42:02,830 --> 00:42:05,960
Father, what are we going to do?

716
00:42:06,130 --> 00:42:09,500
You said you were completely against
us becoming double in-laws.

717
00:42:10,130 --> 00:42:11,130
I'll allow it.

718
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:12,800
What?

719
00:42:13,470 --> 00:42:15,200
Allow it?
What do you mean, allow it?

720
00:42:15,600 --> 00:42:17,370
Gi Cheol's granddaughter
and Hyun Bin,

721
00:42:17,810 --> 00:42:19,840
go ahead with their marriage.

722
00:42:20,180 --> 00:42:23,380
Oh, my goodness, Father. Father, no.

723
00:42:23,780 --> 00:42:26,480
- Just do as I say.
- No, we can't, Father.

724
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,680
Even if you say yes,

725
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:29,790
Dr. Han Seong Mi said
she'd never allow it.

726
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:31,120
That's why...

727
00:42:31,950 --> 00:42:33,490
you need to go
and smooth things over...

728
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,760
with Gi Cheol's daughter-in-law.

729
00:42:35,390 --> 00:42:40,060
What? Why would I do that?
Father, you can't be serious.

730
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:43,400
Don't argue with me.
Just do it. Understand?

731
00:42:43,630 --> 00:42:46,370
Father, I can't.
I really can't do it.

732
00:42:46,440 --> 00:42:47,440
I really can't.

733
00:42:47,970 --> 00:42:49,570
Father? Hello?

734
00:42:51,670 --> 00:42:52,680
There. Satisfied?

735
00:42:58,580 --> 00:42:59,580
Well done.

736
00:43:01,420 --> 00:43:02,420
You scared me.

737
00:43:03,620 --> 00:43:07,160
What? What is it? Honey?
What did Father say?

738
00:43:07,620 --> 00:43:09,790
What? What can't you do?

739
00:43:10,790 --> 00:43:11,790
He told me...

740
00:43:13,630 --> 00:43:16,500
to appease Dr. Han Seong Mi...

741
00:43:19,170 --> 00:43:22,470
and get her permission
for the marriage.

742
00:43:23,740 --> 00:43:24,740
What?

743
00:43:25,410 --> 00:43:26,980
Oh my, is that true?

744
00:43:28,110 --> 00:43:29,110
So...

745
00:43:29,680 --> 00:43:32,150
let's just wait and see
how she handles it, shall we?

746
00:43:39,290 --> 00:43:43,560
I can't do this. I can't!

747
00:43:43,630 --> 00:43:46,560
I won't do it. I'm not
going to. I said no.

748
00:43:46,630 --> 00:43:50,500
Father, I'm not doing this!

749
00:43:51,470 --> 00:43:54,200
I'm not doing it. I don't want to!

750
00:43:55,600 --> 00:43:58,840
I can't. I don't want to.

751
00:43:59,140 --> 00:44:02,880
I'm telling you,
I really can't stand Gong Ju Ah.

752
00:44:03,950 --> 00:44:05,050
Hey, you punk. Yang Hyun Bin.

753
00:44:05,810 --> 00:44:08,820
You turned this house
upside down, you brat.

754
00:44:09,420 --> 00:44:10,420
What?

755
00:44:11,350 --> 00:44:12,450
Where are you right now?

756
00:44:16,660 --> 00:44:17,660
What is this?

757
00:44:18,290 --> 00:44:19,290
What is this strange combination?

758
00:44:19,560 --> 00:44:22,130
Hey, hey. Come sit down, hurry.

759
00:44:22,530 --> 00:44:23,970
- My in-law.
- Good grief.

760
00:44:24,070 --> 00:44:25,070
So, you're here.

761
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:28,200
How did you all
end up here together?

762
00:44:28,500 --> 00:44:31,740
- I went to greet them today.
- What?

763
00:44:32,710 --> 00:44:33,710
You little punk.

764
00:44:34,380 --> 00:44:35,380
You just announce to our family...

765
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:37,210
that you're getting married with
or without our permission...

766
00:44:37,380 --> 00:44:40,220
Grandfather was the one
who told me to go.

767
00:44:40,680 --> 00:44:41,680
Grandfather?

768
00:44:42,250 --> 00:44:43,620
Here you go, Hyun Bin.

769
00:44:44,190 --> 00:44:45,750
Let me pour you a drink.

770
00:44:46,090 --> 00:44:49,960
Wow. I really wanted to accept
a drink from you, Father.

771
00:44:50,130 --> 00:44:52,590
Oh my, don't call me Father yet.
All right?

772
00:44:52,900 --> 00:44:55,160
Besides, as you already know,

773
00:44:55,530 --> 00:44:58,930
the fathers on both sides
have no say in the matter.

774
00:45:02,170 --> 00:45:03,170
It's true.

775
00:45:04,640 --> 00:45:05,640
Hey.

776
00:45:06,210 --> 00:45:09,110
Is there any way we can
get our wives to cool down?

777
00:45:10,650 --> 00:45:15,150
Father. Please come
to the VIP golf event.

778
00:45:15,750 --> 00:45:19,390
- Why?
- Ju Ah says she wants to meet Mom.

779
00:45:20,590 --> 00:45:22,890
Hey, are you sure
that's a good idea?

780
00:45:23,330 --> 00:45:24,590
There won't be
another incident, will there?

781
00:45:26,060 --> 00:45:28,230
You know, the golf ball...

782
00:45:28,560 --> 00:45:30,070
Right in the eye. That incident.

783
00:45:30,600 --> 00:45:32,600
That's right. That.

784
00:45:32,870 --> 00:45:34,270
Oh, come on. No way.

785
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:39,340
- Should I stop them? What now?
- I don't know.

786
00:45:43,180 --> 00:45:44,780
Are you sure you'll be okay?

787
00:45:45,480 --> 00:45:47,150
You can't stand Hyun Bin's mother.

788
00:45:47,750 --> 00:45:48,780
I can't.

789
00:45:49,420 --> 00:45:53,690
But my love for Hyun Bin is
stronger than that feeling.

790
00:45:54,790 --> 00:45:57,760
Can you understand, Grandma?

791
00:46:00,730 --> 00:46:01,730
I can.

792
00:46:04,130 --> 00:46:06,670
Grandma. I have a favor to ask.

793
00:46:07,400 --> 00:46:10,710
What is it? You want me
to convince your mom?

794
00:46:11,110 --> 00:46:12,110
No.

795
00:46:12,370 --> 00:46:14,680
I don't want her to give
her permission reluctantly.

796
00:46:15,380 --> 00:46:17,410
She has her reasons
for being against it,

797
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:19,150
and she's right about everything.

798
00:46:20,380 --> 00:46:24,090
So please, just give her
a little extra attention.

799
00:46:24,550 --> 00:46:27,460
She's in pain and having a hard time
with her radiation therapy.

800
00:46:29,360 --> 00:46:30,360
All right.

801
00:46:30,960 --> 00:46:34,200
But why are you in such a hurry?

802
00:46:34,700 --> 00:46:35,960
Is it because of Mr. Yang?

803
00:46:36,530 --> 00:46:37,530
Yes.

804
00:46:37,870 --> 00:46:40,040
It's not just the bone marrow transplant
that's hard.

805
00:46:40,170 --> 00:46:43,470
Chemotherapy is no small matter
at his age either.

806
00:46:44,810 --> 00:46:46,180
Seeing Hyun Bin get married...

807
00:46:46,240 --> 00:46:48,540
might give him more strength,
don't you think?

808
00:46:51,450 --> 00:46:52,450
You're right.

809
00:47:31,150 --> 00:47:33,190
My aunt found out.

810
00:47:33,590 --> 00:47:35,360
What? That we saw a play?

811
00:47:35,960 --> 00:47:38,730
No. The fact that I like you.

812
00:47:50,910 --> 00:47:53,010
(Woo Jae In-Law)

813
00:47:58,110 --> 00:48:01,380
All right, Yang Eun Bin.
At least there's this.

814
00:48:02,150 --> 00:48:05,090
I even got to hear
Woo Jae say he likes me.

815
00:48:07,220 --> 00:48:08,790
This is enough.

816
00:48:10,060 --> 00:48:11,790
So, let's get a grip.

817
00:48:24,010 --> 00:48:28,410
(Invitational With Phantom Golf)

818
00:48:33,150 --> 00:48:34,880
You said you were
golfing with friends,

819
00:48:34,950 --> 00:48:37,490
- but you brought me here?
- A friend's shop...

820
00:48:38,550 --> 00:48:39,660
Hyun Bin asked me to.

821
00:48:40,160 --> 00:48:42,660
Father, please come with me.
All right?

822
00:48:44,460 --> 00:48:45,460
Let's disappear.

823
00:48:46,560 --> 00:48:47,560
First of all,

824
00:48:47,630 --> 00:48:49,560
thank you for accepting
our invitation.

825
00:48:49,930 --> 00:48:52,930
Was the dedicated car service
comfortable?

826
00:48:53,840 --> 00:48:56,670
Who asked you to send that?
Stop trying to show off.

827
00:48:57,010 --> 00:48:59,540
Showing off?
As your future daughter-in-law,

828
00:48:59,610 --> 00:49:01,580
I can't believe
you'd distort my tearful efforts...

829
00:49:01,640 --> 00:49:04,380
to score points with you,
Mother. I'm so upset.

830
00:49:04,650 --> 00:49:07,080
What? Future daughter-in-law?

831
00:49:07,620 --> 00:49:08,620
Yes, Mother.

832
00:49:08,880 --> 00:49:10,790
So that you're comfortable
during your round,

833
00:49:10,950 --> 00:49:12,620
we've prepared
the best service for you.

834
00:49:12,750 --> 00:49:14,160
Please relax and enjoy yourself.

835
00:49:15,290 --> 00:49:18,160
How dare you be so slick.
This is unbelievable. Seriously.

836
00:49:18,460 --> 00:49:20,500
Then shall we start
with the accessories...

837
00:49:20,560 --> 00:49:22,230
I prepared to your taste, Mother?

838
00:49:23,130 --> 00:49:25,800
- Let's go.
- Let go of me. I said let go.

839
00:49:25,870 --> 00:49:27,670
My, you're so strong.

840
00:49:28,040 --> 00:49:30,670
- Hey, let me go. Unbelievable.
- Right this way, please.

841
00:49:30,670 --> 00:49:31,710
Hello?

842
00:49:32,210 --> 00:49:35,010
I'm Yang Hyun Bin,
and I'll be your host...

843
00:49:35,010 --> 00:49:36,210
for this VIP golf event.

844
00:49:40,620 --> 00:49:43,450
Despite the many recent changes
at FG,

845
00:49:43,690 --> 00:49:45,650
to all of our customers
who have trusted...

846
00:49:45,720 --> 00:49:46,960
our brand and stood by us,

847
00:49:47,060 --> 00:49:48,720
I want to express
my sincere gratitude.

848
00:49:49,060 --> 00:49:50,960
We will continue to do our best...

849
00:49:51,060 --> 00:49:53,900
to provide even better
products and services.

850
00:49:54,630 --> 00:49:56,600
The donations and proceeds
from this event...

851
00:49:56,670 --> 00:49:58,470
will be used to support
orphanages...

852
00:49:58,530 --> 00:50:00,700
and other meaningful causes.

853
00:50:01,000 --> 00:50:04,770
For today, we hope you can put aside
your busy schedules...

854
00:50:04,970 --> 00:50:08,340
and on this beautiful course,
we hope you have an enjoyable game.

855
00:50:16,080 --> 00:50:17,090
You can do it.

856
00:50:17,790 --> 00:50:18,790
Go!

857
00:50:19,960 --> 00:50:20,960
So annoying.

858
00:50:28,560 --> 00:50:29,800
Good shot.

859
00:50:30,430 --> 00:50:33,100
- Good shot.
- She's a great player, isn't she?

860
00:50:36,000 --> 00:50:38,510
Hey, it looks like Ju Ah is
really going for it, right?

861
00:50:38,940 --> 00:50:39,980
It seems so.

862
00:50:45,210 --> 00:50:46,210
Honestly.

863
00:50:47,750 --> 00:50:50,120
You got this.

864
00:50:53,590 --> 00:50:55,960
Good shot. All right.

865
00:51:07,540 --> 00:51:09,770
- Nice one.
- So cool.

866
00:51:19,710 --> 00:51:21,850
- Oh my.
- Oh my.

867
00:51:25,050 --> 00:51:28,290
My. It seems I've saved
you twice now, Mother.

868
00:51:28,560 --> 00:51:31,230
- What do you mean, twice?
- Don't you remember?

869
00:51:31,560 --> 00:51:33,630
At the last event,
when a golf ball flew at your face,

870
00:51:33,700 --> 00:51:37,070
I caught it just like this,
and you avoided a serious accident.

871
00:51:44,510 --> 00:51:45,610
You mean that accident...

872
00:51:45,670 --> 00:51:47,580
where I ended up
rolling on the ground?

873
00:51:48,940 --> 00:51:50,750
If I hadn't caught
the ball back then,

874
00:51:51,010 --> 00:51:54,280
- you would've gotten a black eye.
- What did you say?

875
00:52:01,120 --> 00:52:02,260
Why are you looking at me like that?

876
00:52:03,530 --> 00:52:05,790
Mother, you don't
approve of me, do you?

877
00:52:06,660 --> 00:52:07,800
Do you even have to ask?

878
00:52:08,130 --> 00:52:11,200
- I don't approve of you either.
- What?

879
00:52:11,270 --> 00:52:14,600
But no matter how I think about it,
what can I do...

880
00:52:14,600 --> 00:52:17,410
when my love for Hyun Bin is
greater than my dislike for you?

881
00:52:19,210 --> 00:52:20,780
What? What is she talking about?

882
00:52:32,390 --> 00:52:33,420
Here.

883
00:52:35,790 --> 00:52:36,830
What is this?

884
00:52:37,260 --> 00:52:39,160
It's an in-law conflict
prevention agreement.

885
00:52:39,430 --> 00:52:41,400
It covers
the couple's autonomy, privacy,

886
00:52:41,460 --> 00:52:42,960
holiday arrangements, and so on.

887
00:52:43,030 --> 00:52:44,030
I've laid out the guidelines.

888
00:52:44,030 --> 00:52:46,230
- Please review it.
- It should be fine, right?

889
00:52:48,970 --> 00:52:50,340
Look here, Gong Ju Ah.

890
00:52:50,670 --> 00:52:54,280
I have absolutely no intention
of approving this marriage.

891
00:52:54,740 --> 00:52:56,280
Then we have no choice...

892
00:52:56,340 --> 00:52:58,910
but to run away to
Argentina together.

893
00:52:59,450 --> 00:53:00,450
What?

894
00:53:01,020 --> 00:53:02,580
If you don't give your approval,

895
00:53:02,680 --> 00:53:04,950
I'll assume you never want
to see your son again.

896
00:53:05,750 --> 00:53:09,120
Oh my, look at her.

897
00:53:09,420 --> 00:53:10,530
Just look at her.

898
00:53:13,130 --> 00:53:14,460
That little vixen...

899
00:53:15,030 --> 00:53:16,100
Good grief, what is this?

900
00:53:19,270 --> 00:53:23,370
Wow, an in-law conflict
prevention agreement?

901
00:53:25,370 --> 00:53:27,210
She's Seong Mi's daughter,
all right.

902
00:53:27,740 --> 00:53:28,980
She's so bold and smart.

903
00:53:29,110 --> 00:53:30,510
Honey, don't you think
you're being unfair?

904
00:53:30,980 --> 00:53:32,410
After everything she's done to me?

905
00:53:33,250 --> 00:53:34,580
But after seeing her today,

906
00:53:35,180 --> 00:53:37,290
I can tell Ju Ah really
likes our Hyun Bin too.

907
00:53:38,450 --> 00:53:40,760
It didn't seem like Hyun Bin
was the only one invested.

908
00:53:42,960 --> 00:53:45,860
Honey. Can you defy Father's wishes?

909
00:53:47,560 --> 00:53:50,300
Even if it is Father's wish...

910
00:53:50,670 --> 00:53:51,730
Darling.

911
00:53:51,970 --> 00:53:56,440
You're someone who can live
without me, but not without Father.

912
00:53:56,970 --> 00:53:58,670
So what are you telling me to do?

913
00:53:58,810 --> 00:54:01,380
Just bite the bullet
and go to Seong Mi,

914
00:54:02,480 --> 00:54:05,680
- and beg her just once.
- Are you crazy? Why should I beg?

915
00:54:05,910 --> 00:54:08,680
Then do that thing you do.

916
00:54:10,090 --> 00:54:12,290
"I may be sitting here right now,"

917
00:54:12,490 --> 00:54:13,790
- "but in your mind,"
- But in your mind,

918
00:54:13,860 --> 00:54:14,860
- "please picture me on my knees."
- please picture me on my knees.

919
00:54:15,760 --> 00:54:17,860
- That one.
- Unbelievable.

920
00:54:18,590 --> 00:54:20,560
It'll be epic. Just once.

921
00:54:22,960 --> 00:54:26,200
Hospital volunteering.

922
00:54:28,470 --> 00:54:30,810
This, and also...

923
00:54:32,410 --> 00:54:34,710
What? Are you waiting for a call?

924
00:54:35,910 --> 00:54:38,250
It looks like Ju Ah
went and did something,

925
00:54:38,710 --> 00:54:41,380
but still no word
from Bucket's wife.

926
00:54:42,050 --> 00:54:43,820
Hey, tell me.

927
00:54:44,390 --> 00:54:47,890
If Bucket's wife came to you
and begged profusely,

928
00:54:48,260 --> 00:54:50,330
would you consider
approving the marriage?

929
00:54:50,390 --> 00:54:51,790
I'll have to see how she acts.

930
00:54:52,530 --> 00:54:54,600
She only grovels
when she needs something,

931
00:54:54,660 --> 00:54:55,660
so I can't trust her.

932
00:54:55,730 --> 00:54:59,330
- You're harsh, Han Seong Mi.
- You don't remember?

933
00:55:00,040 --> 00:55:02,040
"I may be sitting here right now,
but in your mind,"

934
00:55:02,100 --> 00:55:03,710
"please picture me on my knees."

935
00:55:04,010 --> 00:55:05,040
That's what she said.

936
00:55:05,940 --> 00:55:09,240
That's right. Bucket did
the exact same imitation for me.

937
00:55:09,410 --> 00:55:12,980
- Seriously.
- If he listens to Bucket's wife,

938
00:55:13,080 --> 00:55:15,680
he has no chance of being
elected city councilman.

939
00:55:16,020 --> 00:55:19,020
Actually, Dong Ik said he'll
only listen to me from now on.

940
00:55:19,420 --> 00:55:22,320
Look. I'm trying to
get Dong Ik elected,

941
00:55:22,390 --> 00:55:26,930
so I'm working on a strategy.
What else is Dong Ik good at?

942
00:55:28,200 --> 00:55:29,200
Yes, that's right.

943
00:55:29,860 --> 00:55:31,630
(Getting Married
Jung Gi Beom and Oh Jin Ah)

944
00:55:31,700 --> 00:55:33,570
Hey, a wedding invitation already?

945
00:55:34,470 --> 00:55:37,610
People move at lightning speed
once they make up their minds.

946
00:55:38,170 --> 00:55:39,840
Well, my Gi Beom,

947
00:55:40,140 --> 00:55:42,940
he ignores the speed limit
and just floors the accelerator.

948
00:55:43,340 --> 00:55:46,050
Of course. When it comes
to my feelings for Jin Ah,

949
00:55:46,720 --> 00:55:47,880
there are no brakes.

950
00:55:50,120 --> 00:55:54,060
Come on. Save that lovey-dovey stuff
for when you two are alone.

951
00:55:54,290 --> 00:55:55,660
Give me some more
of those invitations.

952
00:55:56,060 --> 00:55:57,590
- I'll hand them out at the station.
- Thank you.

953
00:55:57,660 --> 00:55:58,660
Okay.

954
00:55:59,030 --> 00:56:02,030
How many should I give him?
Three, four.

955
00:56:02,100 --> 00:56:03,670
Oh, just give him all of them.

956
00:56:04,270 --> 00:56:05,330
Here you go.

957
00:56:06,070 --> 00:56:07,500
- All of them?
- Yes.

958
00:56:08,940 --> 00:56:11,410
- Thank you.
- Do you have enough for the market?

959
00:56:11,510 --> 00:56:13,410
- We do.
- We have plenty. Plenty.

960
00:56:13,480 --> 00:56:14,840
- Yes.
- You printed a lot, I see.

961
00:56:14,910 --> 00:56:15,910
Come on.

962
00:56:17,150 --> 00:56:19,410
My goodness, congratulations.

963
00:56:19,810 --> 00:56:21,280
I heard you say your wish
was to get married soon...

964
00:56:21,350 --> 00:56:22,420
and become a mother
of many children.

965
00:56:22,580 --> 00:56:24,120
Well, it looks like
it's about to come true.

966
00:56:24,250 --> 00:56:27,290
Gosh, how could you say
that in front of Gi Beom?

967
00:56:27,390 --> 00:56:29,260
It's all right.
To be honest, my wish is to be...

968
00:56:29,320 --> 00:56:30,530
a father of many children too.

969
00:56:30,660 --> 00:56:33,630
Oh, you're a match made in heaven.
You're perfect for each other.

970
00:56:34,560 --> 00:56:36,360
Thank you.
Please come to the wedding...

971
00:56:36,430 --> 00:56:37,670
and give us your blessing.

972
00:56:37,730 --> 00:56:39,230
- Of course.
- Thank you.

973
00:56:39,300 --> 00:56:40,300
Hope you sell a lot.

974
00:56:40,670 --> 00:56:41,670
Then, may I please
have your signature...

975
00:56:41,740 --> 00:56:42,740
for this recommendation?

976
00:56:43,740 --> 00:56:44,810
They must be collecting signatures.

977
00:56:44,870 --> 00:56:47,310
- Thank you.
- We didn't give you an invitation?

978
00:56:47,710 --> 00:56:48,710
Of course not.

979
00:56:49,410 --> 00:56:50,480
- Yes, thank you.
- Want me to tell you...

980
00:56:50,550 --> 00:56:51,580
something funny?

981
00:56:51,650 --> 00:56:53,010
- Yes, thank you. We will...
- What is it?

982
00:56:53,080 --> 00:56:54,280
We will be sure to
protect this market.

983
00:56:54,350 --> 00:56:55,780
Get this.
Dr. Yang's approval rating...

984
00:56:55,820 --> 00:56:56,820
is 0.3 percent.

985
00:56:57,090 --> 00:56:58,220
Zero-point-three percent?

986
00:57:00,390 --> 00:57:01,420
Oh my.

987
00:57:05,490 --> 00:57:09,660
Hey, don't listen to that. Okay?
Hey, don't listen. It's not true.

988
00:57:09,830 --> 00:57:11,970
It's probably gone up to
zero-point-five percent...

989
00:57:12,030 --> 00:57:13,900
by now. It's fine.
You can do it, Dong Ik.

990
00:57:14,340 --> 00:57:16,470
Here are the IR materials
and the event program...

991
00:57:16,540 --> 00:57:17,710
for the business briefing.

992
00:57:17,770 --> 00:57:19,870
(3H Acupressure Bed)

993
00:57:19,970 --> 00:57:22,540
I'll review the event program,

994
00:57:22,610 --> 00:57:24,880
and if there's anything
I want to add or change,

995
00:57:24,950 --> 00:57:26,180
I can do that, right?

996
00:57:26,480 --> 00:57:28,720
Of course. I'd appreciate that.

997
00:57:30,120 --> 00:57:34,290
Did a lot of people sign up
for the briefing?

998
00:57:34,560 --> 00:57:39,460
Of course. The registration rate
is up 20 percent from last year.

999
00:57:40,560 --> 00:57:41,600
Really?

1000
00:57:41,930 --> 00:57:44,070
Oh my, that makes me
a little nervous.

1001
00:57:44,130 --> 00:57:45,130
Come on. From what I saw...

1002
00:57:45,230 --> 00:57:46,870
at the Outstanding Store
awards ceremony,

1003
00:57:46,940 --> 00:57:49,870
you looked like a natural on stage.

1004
00:57:51,340 --> 00:57:53,340
Oh my, was it that obvious?

1005
00:57:55,110 --> 00:57:58,010
I was actually in a beauty pageant.

1006
00:57:59,180 --> 00:58:01,720
No wonder. I thought
you had a special aura...

1007
00:58:01,780 --> 00:58:03,850
about you from the moment I met you.

1008
00:58:03,950 --> 00:58:05,320
Oh, you're too kind.

1009
00:58:07,220 --> 00:58:09,390
- Oh, one moment. I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

1010
00:58:10,690 --> 00:58:11,890
Onjeong Real Estate?

1011
00:58:14,260 --> 00:58:15,300
Yes, hello.

1012
00:58:18,170 --> 00:58:20,370
My father-in-law
is traveling right now.

1013
00:58:21,140 --> 00:58:22,300
But what is this about?

1014
00:58:28,840 --> 00:58:32,150
He specifically told me
not to tell anyone,

1015
00:58:32,480 --> 00:58:35,350
but I can't reach him
and I need his official seal.

1016
00:58:36,750 --> 00:58:39,320
Why did he suddenly decide
to sell the building?

1017
00:58:39,720 --> 00:58:41,820
And why did he tell her
not to tell anyone?

1018
00:58:43,560 --> 00:58:46,360
Where is that seal?

1019
00:58:59,510 --> 00:59:02,710
Oh my, when did he take
a picture like this?

1020
00:59:03,040 --> 00:59:04,910
Why take a picture like
a funeral portrait...

1021
00:59:06,680 --> 00:59:08,620
Let's get Hyun Bin married.

1022
00:59:09,380 --> 00:59:10,650
I'm counting on you.

1023
00:59:10,650 --> 00:59:12,950
My one remaining wish
while I'm still alive...

1024
00:59:13,960 --> 00:59:15,360
is that one thing.

1025
00:59:20,060 --> 00:59:21,660
No, it can't be.

1026
00:59:24,330 --> 00:59:25,630
Anyway, everyone hurry.

1027
00:59:26,200 --> 00:59:27,700
Se Ri, hurry up and get him married.

1028
00:59:27,700 --> 00:59:29,340
And you, make something
of yourself quickly.

1029
00:59:30,000 --> 00:59:32,040
I don't have time.

1030
00:59:34,110 --> 00:59:35,810
I'm just saying to set him up
with any woman.

1031
00:59:36,380 --> 00:59:38,210
Father.

1032
00:59:38,380 --> 00:59:41,020
Have I asked you for that much?
How can you say you can't do it?

1033
00:59:43,050 --> 00:59:44,050
No.

1034
00:59:44,950 --> 00:59:46,050
It can't be.

1035
00:59:47,360 --> 00:59:48,420
Grandfather is leaving on...

1036
00:59:48,420 --> 00:59:49,590
a cross-country trip
starting tomorrow.

1037
00:59:50,120 --> 00:59:51,730
I'm sending him on the trip.

1038
01:00:02,300 --> 01:00:05,310
(Executive Director Pacu Nacho)

1039
01:00:09,110 --> 01:00:10,180
Yes, Mother.

1040
01:00:10,450 --> 01:00:11,480
Yang Hyun Bin.

1041
01:00:12,310 --> 01:00:13,510
About your grandfather's trip...

1042
01:00:14,080 --> 01:00:15,250
Where did you send him?

1043
01:00:15,720 --> 01:00:19,090
What? Oh, here and there.

1044
01:00:19,090 --> 01:00:21,020
Stop being vague and tell me.

1045
01:00:22,220 --> 01:00:24,060
Something's wrong with
Grandfather, isn't there?

1046
01:00:27,760 --> 01:00:29,060
What is it?

1047
01:00:32,530 --> 01:00:33,840
Tell me, Hyun Bin.

1048
01:00:35,240 --> 01:00:37,910
Tell me.
I said, tell me now, Hyun Bin.

1049
01:00:40,340 --> 01:00:41,410
Well...

1050
01:00:47,650 --> 01:00:50,520
Grandfather has acute leukemia.

1051
01:00:51,020 --> 01:00:52,820
A bone marrow transplant,
chemotherapy...

1052
01:00:53,120 --> 01:00:55,260
at his age, it'll be too
much for him to endure.

1053
01:00:55,860 --> 01:00:58,730
That's why he was in such a rush
about everything.

1054
01:01:04,070 --> 01:01:05,070
What am I going to do?

1055
01:01:19,010 --> 01:01:21,020
What am I going to do...

1056
01:01:28,960 --> 01:01:30,790
What am I going to do...

1057
01:01:48,480 --> 01:01:50,580
Hey, what are you doing here?

1058
01:01:50,880 --> 01:01:54,950
Hyun Bin is busy today,
so I came instead.

1059
01:01:55,520 --> 01:01:57,350
You're making me uncomfortable.
Please just go.

1060
01:01:57,620 --> 01:01:59,320
You'll have to put up with it.

1061
01:01:59,590 --> 01:02:00,720
If I'm good to you,

1062
01:02:00,790 --> 01:02:03,620
Hyun Bin will also be good
to my grandfather, right?

1063
01:02:05,230 --> 01:02:06,230
You're a sharp one.

1064
01:02:07,860 --> 01:02:10,300
You haven't eaten anything,
have you? One second.

1065
01:02:13,070 --> 01:02:16,070
Ta-da. Guess what this is.

1066
01:02:16,370 --> 01:02:17,570
Is it something tasty?

1067
01:02:18,110 --> 01:02:19,140
That's right.

1068
01:02:19,540 --> 01:02:22,140
I bought some canned fruit,
snacks, and a few other things.

1069
01:02:22,210 --> 01:02:24,380
I only brought things
the hospital said were okay,

1070
01:02:24,450 --> 01:02:25,950
so you can eat them
without worrying.

1071
01:02:26,450 --> 01:02:27,450
And...

1072
01:02:28,980 --> 01:02:29,980
Ta-da.

1073
01:02:30,180 --> 01:02:33,490
My hair has been thinning,
so I actually needed this.

1074
01:02:33,550 --> 01:02:37,020
Oh, perfect.
Shall I help you put it on?

1075
01:02:37,890 --> 01:02:42,260
Okay. Let's get you looking sharp.

1076
01:02:43,460 --> 01:02:46,600
Wow, you look so handsome.
Just a moment.

1077
01:02:46,600 --> 01:02:48,740
Here, would you like to
look in the mirror?

1078
01:02:49,740 --> 01:02:52,070
Wow, that color
looks so good on you.

1079
01:02:52,140 --> 01:02:54,610
Let's take a picture of this
and show it to Hyun Bin.

1080
01:02:54,880 --> 01:02:57,210
Come on, let's make
Hyun Bin jealous.

1081
01:02:58,010 --> 01:02:59,310
One, two.

1082
01:03:00,380 --> 01:03:02,550
Wow, you look great in it.

1083
01:03:12,790 --> 01:03:13,790
Se Ri...

1084
01:03:14,560 --> 01:03:15,560
Se Ri.

1085
01:03:19,130 --> 01:03:20,840
- Thank you.
- Oh, it's nothing.

1086
01:03:20,940 --> 01:03:22,400
- Thank you.
- We'll come again next week. Okay.

1087
01:03:22,470 --> 01:03:23,470
Take care.

1088
01:03:24,210 --> 01:03:27,280
<i>- Live with love</i>
<i>- Live with love</i>

1089
01:03:28,640 --> 01:03:30,510
Wow, I didn't know
you do volunteer work...

1090
01:03:30,580 --> 01:03:31,750
like this after your job.

1091
01:03:31,810 --> 01:03:33,980
Yes. Others might call it childish,
but see?

1092
01:03:34,050 --> 01:03:36,020
They love it
when we sing to them, right?

1093
01:03:38,720 --> 01:03:42,460
- What?
- Being out here feels much better.

1094
01:03:42,520 --> 01:03:43,960
- Right?
- Ju Ah...

1095
01:03:44,030 --> 01:03:46,330
- So much better.
- That's right.

1096
01:03:46,890 --> 01:03:50,330
Oh my, it's gotten crowded
now that it's the afternoon.

1097
01:03:50,930 --> 01:03:52,770
The view is nice.

1098
01:03:53,030 --> 01:03:54,600
- What?
- Oh my.

1099
01:04:09,950 --> 01:04:11,620
I was wondering when you'd get here.

1100
01:04:12,650 --> 01:04:14,790
Were you waiting for me?

1101
01:04:15,360 --> 01:04:17,330
I heard Mr. Yang told you to come...

1102
01:04:17,390 --> 01:04:19,030
and smooth things over with me.

1103
01:04:21,060 --> 01:04:22,300
When you didn't show up,

1104
01:04:22,560 --> 01:04:25,670
I assumed you had no intention
of letting our kids get married.

1105
01:04:27,600 --> 01:04:29,440
No, that is not it. I do.

1106
01:04:30,810 --> 01:04:32,770
I will smooth things
over with you, Dr. Han.

1107
01:04:33,110 --> 01:04:35,810
Well, even though we are
just sitting here like this,

1108
01:04:36,140 --> 01:04:38,380
am I supposed to pretend
you are kneeling?

1109
01:04:49,290 --> 01:04:51,430
Seriously? What are you doing?

1110
01:05:26,860 --> 01:05:29,660
(Recipe For Love)

1111
01:05:29,760 --> 01:05:32,600
I wrote down the pros and cons
of marrying Hyun Bin.

1112
01:05:32,670 --> 01:05:35,500
As I was writing, I realized
there are quite a few cons.

1113
01:05:35,640 --> 01:05:39,310
We have to think about it
from Ju Ah's perspective.

1114
01:05:39,940 --> 01:05:42,210
What if we use your concept
for the PR, Jeong Han?

1115
01:05:42,280 --> 01:05:44,710
- We can even hit 30 percent. Hey.
- Let's go for it.

1116
01:05:44,780 --> 01:05:46,950
She says she cannot stand
that those two know.

1117
01:05:47,420 --> 01:05:49,520
We can't be the ones to tell them.

1118
01:05:49,520 --> 01:05:50,580
What did you say?

1119
01:05:51,420 --> 01:05:52,420
Really?
